locality: Reserve de Waza, c. 40 km S. of Waza.

Dindéfello. Trail to the waterfall. Gallery forest with Ceiba pentandra along permanent stream.
Some km SE of Tenkodogo. Fallow vegetation dominated by Piliostigma and seasonally inundated grass-land on poor soils.
Waza National Park, W of Bodelaram.

45 km SW Sikasso, 2 km NNE du village Lobougoula.
